00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:56,640
I thought to myself, what I could do?

582
00:23:56,960 --> 00:23:57,790
Find a doctor.

583
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:01,710
Yeah, you're smart.

584
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:03,630
And I

585
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,400
went and got a hammer

586
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:08,960
and tried to break it.

587
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,550
But then I thought,

588
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:13,310
if I broke it

589
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,920
and got it in my mouth,

590
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:17,200
I'd have hurt my face.

591
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:19,960
If my classmates asked about it...

592
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:20,710
Look,

593
00:24:20,990 --> 00:24:22,160
the scars on our faces

594
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,920
are from fights.

595
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:25,360
We're courageous and brave.

596
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:26,880
Look at you.

597
00:24:27,230 --> 00:24:28,750
And you swallowed a light bulb!

598
00:24:31,510 --> 00:24:32,920
Then I thought,

599
00:24:33,470 --> 00:24:34,990
why didn't I just

600
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:37,510
swallow the bulb?

601
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:38,880
Alright, done.

602
00:24:39,360 --> 00:24:40,070
Feel it.

603
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:41,640
Does it still hurt?

604
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:46,070
So, did you swallow it?

605
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:47,750
No.

606
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,270
I found a doctor too.

607
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:51,030
Give me an anesthetic and I was fine.

608
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,030
Dai Qiangqiang!

609
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:53,790
Grandma!

610
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:55,160
Grandma!

611
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:55,990
You've grown up.

612
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,030
How did you get a bottle

613
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:58,120
in your mouth?

614
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,070
Someone else

615
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,120
left this drink on a chair.

616
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:02,550
I've never had one.

617
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,160
I just wanted to try it.

618
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:05,920
Then...

619
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,600
Thanks, Doctor!

620
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:08,440
You're welcome.

621
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,160
Zhou.

622
00:25:09,470 --> 00:25:11,070
Relief of swollen tongue
with prohormones.

623
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:11,790
Alright.

624
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:12,680
Does he need to stay?

625
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:13,270
No need.

626
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:13,990
Remember.

627
00:25:14,230 --> 00:25:15,070
If the swelling doesn't go down

628
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,400
tomorrow morning,

629
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,030
come to the hospital right away.

630
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:18,400
Okay.

631
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:19,200
Thank you, Doctor.

632
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,470
Come on, thank the doctor.

633
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:22,190
Thank you, Doctor.

634
00:25:22,230 --> 00:25:22,750
Thank you.

635
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:26,070
What's this drink?

636
00:25:26,550 --> 00:25:27,470
Is it that good?

637
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,160
No.

638
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:29,960
Grandma.

639
00:25:30,270 --> 00:25:31,750
I won't drink it anymore.

640
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:34,600
Really that bad?

641
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,910
I'll buy a bottle tomorrow

642
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:37,990
and see how bad it tastes.

643
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:40,990
Let's go and get the medicine.

644
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,120
Alright. Thanks.

645
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:44,840
Good work.

646
00:25:51,710 --> 00:25:52,990
What's wrong? What's on your mind?

647
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,970
You're seldom forbearing

648
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:56,310
with a patient.

649
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:57,880
I thought this kid

650
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:58,860
was smart.

651
00:25:58,880 --> 00:25:59,710
And he knew to come to the hospital

652
00:25:59,750 --> 00:26:00,400
for help.

653
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,840
Is it true that you swallowed
a light bulb?

654
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:11,230
What do you think?

655
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:12,710
It's real.

656
00:26:21,990 --> 00:26:22,400
Hello.

657
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,230
Total is 15,700.

658
00:26:27,780 --> 00:26:30,180
[Younger brother: Where are you, bro?
Why didn't you answer the phone?]

659
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:35,510
[Younger brother]
Where are you, bro?

660
00:26:35,510 --> 00:26:36,710
Why didn't you answer the phone?

661
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,230
I'm paying back more

662
00:26:38,230 --> 00:26:39,270
this month than last.

663
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:41,920
Bro.

664
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,510
You can't just leave me alone.

665
00:26:44,030 --> 00:26:44,880
If we wait, the loan collectors

666
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,030
will come to the school again.

667
00:26:46,510 --> 00:26:48,120
Sir, are you going to pay the bill?

668
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,310
There's a queue behind you.

669
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:51,750
Sir.

670
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:54,680
I'm not paying it yet.

671
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:55,400
Sorry about that.

672
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:00,270
Brother.

673
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,600
You finally picked up the phone.

674
00:27:03,120 --> 00:27:04,200
I thought you'd leave me alone.

675
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,070
I was in such a panic.

676
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,440
No, I've been too busy
these past two days.

677
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:09,360
Um...

678
00:27:09,360 --> 00:27:10,310
About that, brother.

679
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:12,160
When will you send me the money?

680
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,440
This issue was due two days ago.

681
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:20,700
[Registered Charge]

682
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:23,030
Brother.

683
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:25,960
Can you hold off on this issue?

684
00:27:27,990 --> 00:27:28,840
For how long?

685
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:30,750
Just a month.

686
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:31,840
Brother.

687
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,070
I've been overdue

688
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:33,990
for almost half a month.

689
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,920
I really can't put it off any longer.

690
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,200
If this keeps up,

691
00:27:37,310 --> 00:27:38,750
it's going to hurt my credit.

692
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:43,420
[Mute]

693
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:47,640
Brother.

694
00:27:47,990 --> 00:27:49,960
Why aren't you talking?

695
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,750
Do you still want to abandon me, right?

696
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,360
Everyone in the family hates me.

697
00:27:54,470 --> 00:27:55,710
You don't like me too, am I right?

698
00:27:56,120 --> 00:27:56,710
Brother!

699
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:58,030
Brother!

700
00:27:58,790 --> 00:28:00,030
Say something!

701
00:28:01,230 --> 00:28:01,840
Brother!

702
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:09,360
I understand.

703
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,470
I'll transfer it to you in a minute.

704
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,200
Thank you, brother.

705
00:28:12,230 --> 00:28:13,440
I know you are the best to me.

706
00:28:14,230 --> 00:28:15,120
Goodbye.

707
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:15,750
Bye.

708
00:28:38,030 --> 00:28:38,790
Where is Fan Tianshui?

709
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:39,880
I don't know.

710
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:40,750
He was just there.

711
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:42,990
He got away just like that?

712
00:28:42,990 --> 00:28:43,880
How did you look after him?

713
00:28:45,550 --> 00:28:46,160
Where are you going?

714
00:28:46,550 --> 00:28:47,230
I'll check the address he registered

715
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:47,960
when he was hospitalized.

716
00:28:48,160 --> 00:28:48,920
Then? He has no money.

717
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:49,790
You're paying for his surgery?

718
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:50,640
People from Chang Feng said

719
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,470
if we use their consumables,

720
00:28:51,470 --> 00:28:52,310
they will provide the surgical fee.

721
00:28:52,790 --> 00:28:53,270
Do you think your father

722
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:53,840
would approve of this?

723
00:28:53,990 --> 00:28:54,920
As long as the president agrees.

724
00:28:54,990 --> 00:28:55,840
Hua will not agree to it.

725
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:57,400
Then take it out of my paycheck.

726
00:28:57,600 --> 00:28:58,070
Whatever it takes,

727
00:28:58,230 --> 00:29:00,070
I want to prove
that we didn't misdiagnose.

728
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:10,550
588.

729
00:29:10,600 --> 00:29:11,510
Here it is.

730
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:23,200
We were sleepless for days

731
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:24,550
trying to find out
what was wrong with you,

732
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:25,640
and you just left like that?

733
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:26,920
That's not very nice, is it?

734
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:38,790
I'm sorry.

735
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:41,120
I just can't afford it.

736
00:29:41,310 --> 00:29:42,400
It's okay. From me...

737
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,200
I'll show you the way.

738
00:29:44,550 --> 00:29:45,360
Sign for a body donation.

739
00:29:46,470 --> 00:29:47,680
If the operation is successful,

740
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:49,070
you'll pay the hospital back

741
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,230
in installments like Yu Yunxia.

742
00:29:52,920 --> 00:29:53,440
Fan Tianshui!

743
00:29:58,310 --> 00:29:59,070
Quick! Call the ambulance!

744
00:29:59,070 --> 00:29:59,600
Alright.

745
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:05,140
[Operating]

746
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:54,310
Come in.

747
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,160
Why are you not in the observation room?

748
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:10,400
What's there to observe?

749
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,750
I'm not a gastroenterologist.

750
00:31:13,270 --> 00:31:14,790
Besides, I couldn't do it

751
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:16,880
even if I was one.

752
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:27,720
I've heard that your hands...

753
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:28,550
It's psychological.

754
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:32,470
Have you seen a psychiatrist?

755
00:31:32,990 --> 00:31:33,440
I have.

756
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,230
What did they say?

757
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:36,400
It's useless.

758
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:44,070
Actually, I'm quite envious of you.

759
00:31:45,120 --> 00:31:45,750
Even though Huangya

760
00:31:45,750 --> 00:31:46,920
did your dad a terrible disservice,

761
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:49,440
he's still alive at least.

762
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,510
You've still got a chance
to operate on him.

763
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:55,030
If only mine was alive.

764
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:57,920
I don't care what the disease is

765
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:00,070
or what the surgery is,

766
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,360
just let me try it once

767
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,440
and maybe I'll get my hand back.

768
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:12,880
I can't help
but think that once in a while.

769
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:19,840
Do you know about Da Vinci's arm?

770
00:32:19,840 --> 00:32:20,640
I do.

771
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,310
It's useless.

772
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,600
It will still shake.

773
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,230
I'm really fine.

774
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,120
All the bad feelings

775
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,200
of dismay and frustration

776
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:32,470
were over two years ago.

777
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:36,030
At least I haven't lost my skill
as a doctor.

778
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:39,310
Now I'm just staying afloat

779
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:40,310
in the Emergency Department.

780
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,160
Let's go with the flow.

781
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,640
You are not running away

782
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,440
from the patient.

783
00:33:00,710 --> 00:33:01,680
So, you are still a good doctor.

784
00:33:28,820 --> 00:33:30,660
[Outpatient]

785
00:33:31,180 --> 00:33:32,060
[Haicheng Everyday]

786
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:33,680
Wang.

787
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:34,270
Yes?

788
00:33:34,270 --> 00:33:34,990
The last story was pretty

789
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:35,640
well received.

790
00:33:35,710 --> 00:33:36,680
Let's move on to a second one.

791
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,310
Why the same disease

792
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:39,840
would have different treatment options?

793
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:41,030
Why do all kinds of tests

794
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:42,600
once you're in the hospital?

795
00:33:43,070 --> 00:33:44,880
What's the difference between

796
00:33:45,030 --> 00:33:45,920
half a yuan and 50,000?

797
00:33:45,990 --> 00:33:46,920
No, wait a minute.

798
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,470
Wait a minute.

799
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:48,990
We are going to the hospital
to expose them.

800
00:33:49,030 --> 00:33:50,200
Will they let us film them?

801
00:33:51,030 --> 00:33:52,960
Ms. Su invited us here.

802
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:55,400
Wait.

803
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,750
Could it be a trap?

804
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:59,740
[Director's Office]

805
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:05,480
Hello, Ms. Su.

806
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,680
I'm a reporter of Haicheng Everyday,

807
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:07,310
Sun Zeli.

808
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:08,030
Hello.

809
00:34:08,510 --> 00:34:09,990
It's a pleasure to have you on board.

810
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:10,670
The pleasure is mine.

811
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:11,400
Come on in, please.

812
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:12,630
I'm all set.

813
00:34:15,340 --> 00:34:17,760
[Healthcare in the eyes of the people]

814
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,280
I watched

815
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,360
your first issue.

816
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,400
You've raised a query.

817
00:34:22,240 --> 00:34:22,990
What's the difference between

818
00:34:23,030 --> 00:34:24,280
half a yuan and 50,000?

819
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,670
They were both diarrhea for five years.

820
00:34:26,990 --> 00:34:28,280
So today is the day.

821
00:34:29,110 --> 00:34:30,030
I want to say a few words.

822
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:34,990
Here you go.

823
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:38,920
Diagnosis

824
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,920
is a headache

825
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,440
for every doctor.

826
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:44,920
Especially diagnosis of rare diseases.

827
00:34:45,240 --> 00:34:46,720
The symptoms may look the same,

828
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:48,400
but the diagnosis and treatment

829
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:49,760
can be very different.

830
00:34:52,030 --> 00:34:53,360
We have two cases now.

831
00:34:53,990 --> 00:34:54,520
One of them only needed

832
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:55,400
less than one yuan's worth

833
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,550
of metronidazole.

834
00:34:57,070 --> 00:34:58,990
The other one needed surgery.

835
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:01,440
That's because
there are different treatments

836
00:35:01,990 --> 00:35:03,400
for different conditions.

837
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:05,150
See.

838
00:35:07,030 --> 00:35:08,590
Here's a list of diarrhea cases

839
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,920
I've had put together.

840
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,420
We have over 200 cases a year

841
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:12,840
in Haicheng Hospital alone.

842
00:35:13,110 --> 00:35:15,020
And it is precisely
because the cause is different,

843
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,320
the treatment method is different,

844
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:18,960
so the cost is also different.

845
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,240
I'm not

846
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,360
a doctor by training.

847
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,400
So I can better understand

848
00:35:23,550 --> 00:35:25,110
what you and the patients
are going through.

849
00:35:25,470 --> 00:35:26,280
In the face of confusion,

850
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,960
the only solution

851
00:35:28,630 --> 00:35:29,880
is the popularization of science.

852
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:31,920
Patiently answering questions

853
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,550
in detail.

854
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:34,880
But now it's a news flash

855
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:36,190
in 15 seconds.

856
00:35:36,470 --> 00:35:37,760
It's impossible to explain.

857
00:35:38,510 --> 00:35:39,560
And in-depth reading

858
00:35:39,630 --> 00:35:41,030
is not something most viewers

859
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,240
have the patience for these days.

860
00:35:43,990 --> 00:35:44,760
That depends on whether you're

861
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,840
reporting this

862
00:35:46,670 --> 00:35:48,550
to really clear up the confusion

863
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:51,150
or because you just want a hot topic.

864
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,150
We have a patient with diarrhea

865
00:35:58,470 --> 00:35:59,990
in Haicheng Hospital today.

866
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,360
Doctors of gastroenterology

867
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,550
are operating on him.

868
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:03,400
I will

869
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:04,070
make an exception

870
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,070
and invite you to observe it

871
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:07,240
and find out about it.

